Insight¶

  • rating_ratio and ratio_numerator have a correlation of 1 because one is based on another.
  • There is a strong positive correlation between retweet_count and favorite_count (0.92) as mentioned in analysis 2.
  • There is negative correlation between p1_conf and both p2_conf (-0.51) and p3_conf (-0.71), this might be due to prediction model having a high confidence in P1 results compared to P2 and P3 results.
